_sText:
This map started out with a simple idea and quickly got out of hand. It is most fun played in deathmatch setting. I really enjoyed creating certain aspects of this map. I should mention it is my first attempt at this.

I personally love the feel and overall darkness to it but realize some may have a hard time seeing everything at times. I recommend nightvision! Also if I get enough requests I am willing to make a daytime version..

Feedback would be greatly appreciated.

Enjoy!
